description: The SWAN Coordinating Center provides SWAN data access to SWAN Investigators through the study website. The SWAN website provides access to longitudinal data describing the physical, biological, psychological, and social changes that occur during the menopausal transition. Data collected from 3,302 SWAN participants from Baseline through the 13th Follow-Up visit are currently available.
title: Study of Womens Health Across the Nation (SWAN) Data: Investigator Access
